reviewText: This is the most hilarious stand-up comedy I have ever seen! Please release the DVD!

Great as usual from bill, my gf and I rolled laughing at this over the top masterpiece. It's comedy which is poking fun at some bad situations and pulls it off without a hitch. If your a avid disney fan this is not for you

Every young man, needs to watch this. I stumbled across this on YouTube about 1 1/2 ago. Since then, I've listed to every bit of material I can from Bill. In my opinion, this is his best work, no holding back, brutally honest, comedy. I REALLY want a hard copy of this special.
